## Artifactory system.yaml - Auto-generated by DevOpsAgent
## Artifactory 7.x 强制要求 PostgreSQL, 不再支持 Derby
## PostgreSQL 18 cluster is on port 5433 (not default 5432)

shared:
  database:
    type: postgresql
    driver: org.postgresql.Driver
    url: jdbc:postgresql://172.18.0.1:5433/artifactory
    username: artifactory
    password: artifactory_secret
